---
---

<section id="about" class="py-20 bg-[var(--color-bg-alt)]">
  <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6">
    <div class="about-panel">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold tracking-tight mb-6">站点设定</h2>

      <p class="about-solo mb-6">
        以时间感知驱动智能工程
      </p>

      <blockquote class="border-l-3 border-[var(--color-brand)] pl-5 text-[var(--color-text-secondary)] text-lg mb-6 about-manifesto">
        <span class="manifesto-signal">CORE SIGNAL</span>
        <span class="manifesto-text">复杂性永远来自真实业务，而工程师的任务是为复杂系统建立可执行的时间坐标。</span>
      </blockquote>

      <p class="text-[var(--color-text-secondary)] leading-relaxed max-w-3xl">
        <strong class="text-[var(--color-text)]">AI克塞号 / AI Kosei</strong> 是我的个人工程站点。
        这里记录 AI 场景化落地、系统架构演进、以及从问题到交付的完整任务日志。
        我关注的核心是 <span class="about-keyword">高可靠性</span>、<span class="about-keyword">可维护性</span> 和 <span class="about-keyword">可迭代速度</span>。
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .about-panel {
    position: relative;
    padding: 2rem;
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    border-radius: 1rem;
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
    box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(2, 132, 199, 0.06);
  }

  .about-solo {
    font-size: clamp(1.35rem, 3.4vw, 2rem);
    font-weight: 800;
    line-height: 1.3;
    color: #0b3b61;
  }

  .about-keyword {
    color: #0b67a2;
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  .about-manifesto {
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .manifesto-signal {
    display: inline-block;
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.72rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.18em;
    color: var(--color-brand);
    margin-bottom: 0.55rem;
    opacity: 0.9;
  }

  .manifesto-text {
    display: block;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: #164e7a;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, #1e3a5f 0%, #0284c7 45%, #06b6d4 55%, #1e3a5f 100%);
    background-size: 220% 100%;
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    background-clip: text;
    animation: manifestoGlow 6s ease-in-out infinite;
  }

  .about-manifesto::after {
    content: "";
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: -30%;
    width: 28%;
    height: 100%;
    background: linear-gradient(110deg, transparent 0%, rgba(6, 182, 212, 0.18) 50%, transparent 100%);
    transform: skewX(-18deg);
    animation: manifestoShine 3.2s ease-in-out 0.8s 1 both;
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  .about-manifesto::before {
    content: "";
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    right: 0;
    top: 0;
    height: 1px;
    background: rgba(2, 132, 199, 0.35);
    box-shadow: 0 0 8px rgba(6, 182, 212, 0.25);
    animation: manifestoScan 5.2s ease-in-out infinite;
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  @keyframes manifestoShine {
    0% {
      left: -35%;
      opacity: 0;
    }

    15% {
      opacity: 1;
    }

    70% {
      opacity: 1;
    }

    100% {
      left: 112%;
      opacity: 0;
    }
  }

  @keyframes manifestoGlow {
    0%, 100% {
      background-position: 100% 50%;
      filter: saturate(98%);
    }

    50% {
      background-position: 0% 50%;
      filter: saturate(122%);
    }
  }

  @keyframes manifestoScan {
    0%, 100% {
      transform: translateY(0);
      opacity: 0.15;
    }

    45% {
      opacity: 0.55;
    }

    50% {
      transform: translateY(3.8rem);
      opacity: 0.65;
    }

    55% {
      opacity: 0.35;
    }
  }
</style>
